Requirements for system users and their's accounts (version 1.0 / 2017.03.04)

Each user

1. must have account in library system
2. must have login/password (for entering in account)
3. 's account must have 'unique identifier'
4. 's account must have 'user type' (e.g. visitor, admin)
5. 's account must record user's personal information (name, surname, etc)


Each 'user type' 'visitor'

1. must record information about borrowed library materials (what, when, for how long etc)


Each 'user type' 'admin'

1. must be able to edit any 'visitor's records about borrowed library materials
